'''''Mama Needs Her New Pair of Shu''''' is a tournament module set in ''Malatra – Living Jungle'' using the ''Dungeons & Dragons'' 2{{rd}} edition ruleset. It is part of the ''[[Living Jungle]]'' series of adventures published for the RPGA Network,  and the third in the ''Shu'' series, following ''[[If the Shu Fits]]'' and ''[[The Soulless Shu]]'' adventures. It is intended for 1{{st}} through 5{{th}} Level characters.

{{Quote|''The [[Simbuki]] tribe of [[Shu]] have seen their Chief [[Wutuka]] pass his crown to the outsider [[Booda]], one with
bad luck. Bad things have happened in the two years he has been chief, but nothing bad is going to happen now, is it? An adventure for heroes of levels 1-5.''|}}

